---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Start Here"
  description="New to Love Over Exile? Start here — a curated guide to the most important resources depending on where you are in your experience of parental alienation."
>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">New here?</p>
      <h1>Start Here</h1>
      <p class="intro">
        This is the place to begin if you've just found Love Over Exile.
        Depending on where you are in your experience, a different starting point will help most.
      </p>

      <div class="start-paths">
        <div class="path-card card">
          <div class="path-when">If you're in the acute phase right now...</div>
          <h3>Get the Free Survival Guide</h3>
          <p>If contact has just broken down or you're in the middle of a legal battle, start with the practical guide. It covers what to do (and what to avoid) in the first weeks and months.</p>
          <a href="/free-guide" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top:1rem;">Get the Free Guide →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="path-card card">
          <div class="path-when">If you're trying to understand what's happening...</div>
          <h3>Understanding Parental Alienation</h3>
          <p>If you're not sure whether what you're experiencing is parental alienation, or you need to understand it more clearly — to explain it to a judge, a therapist, or yourself — start here.</p>
          <a href="/understanding" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top:1rem;">Start Understanding →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="path-card card">
          <div class="path-when">If you're in the long game and looking for meaning...</div>
          <h3>Inner Freedom</h3>
          <p>If the acute legal phase is behind you but the pain and uncertainty remain, and you're trying to rebuild your life while staying open to your child — this is where to go.</p>
          <a href="/inner-freedom" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top:1rem;">Explore Inner Freedom →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="path-card card">
          <div class="path-when">If you need to talk to people who understand...</div>
          <h3>Join the Community</h3>
          <p>The Love Over Exile community is a forum for alienated parents — moderated, real, and free. Sometimes what you need most is to be heard by someone who has lived it.</p>
          <a href="/community" class="btn btn-outline" style="margin-top:1rem;">Join the Community →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="divider" style="margin-block:3rem;" />

      <div class="start-about">
        <h2>About this site</h2>
        <p>
          Love Over Exile is built around a book by Malcolm Smith — an alienated father who
          documented his experience, what he learned, and what helped. The site brings together
          the book's content, a community forum, and free resources.
        </p>
        <p>
          Everything here is free. The book will be available soon — join the waitlist to be
          first to know.
        </p>
        <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top:1.5rem;">
          <a href="/about" class="btn btn-outline">About Malcolm →</a>
          <a href="/the-book" class="btn btn-outline">About the Book →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
.eyebrow {
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--color-amber);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.intro {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  color: var(--color-charcoal-mid);
  margin-bottom: 3rem;
  line-height: 1.7;
}
.start-paths {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
.path-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
.path-when {
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--color-warm-grey);
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.path-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.path-card p { font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--color-charcoal-mid); line-height: 1.65; flex:1; margin: 0; }

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .start-paths { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>
